21
00:04:12,567 --> 00:04:15,067
You know something, right?

22
00:04:15,067 --> 00:04:17,777
- Why aren't you saying anything? 
 - Sung Min...

23
00:04:17,777 --> 00:04:20,147
You saw him a few days ago, too, Sunbae.

24
00:04:20,147 --> 00:04:23,437
Something was definitely up with Shim Hyung Woo!

25
00:04:25,167 --> 00:04:27,467
I should have forced him to tell me then

26
00:04:27,467 --> 00:04:30,197
