56
00:06:07,227 --> 00:06:10,937
Who... is that?

57
00:07:03,877 --> 00:07:06,267
 Here! 

58
00:07:09,987 --> 00:07:11,597
What's wrong?

59
00:07:12,917 --> 00:07:14,787
Are you okay?

60
00:07:24,277 --> 00:07:26,407
 Only burn the warehouse. 

61
00:07:26,407 --> 00:07:28,147
 Leave this behind. 

62
00:07:30,717 --> 00:07:34,077
 - The order was... 
 - I'll take care of it so do as I say. 

63
00:07:59,680 --> 00:08:02,550
   

64
