If you wait for the right time as the second major shareholder

70
00:08:49,517 --> 00:08:51,450
of Sangah Group, I will–

71
00:08:51,450 --> 00:08:53,680
 If it was undercover, maybe. 

72
00:08:53,687 --> 00:08:56,857
But it's too boring to wait without doing anything.

73
00:08:56,857 --> 00:09:00,867
What are you planning?

74
00:09:00,867 --> 00:09:02,617
A plan?

75
00:09:03,107 --> 00:09:06,157
Will a plan be needed for the idiotic father and son,

76
00:09:06,157 --> 00:09:08,787
Lee Chan Joo and Lee Bo Sung?

77
00:09:18,027 --> 00:09:21,947
 The customer is not answering the phone. You'll be connected to voicemail. 

78
00:09:21,947 --> 00:09:24,367
Is he really busy?

79
00:09:27,620 --> 00:09:29,950
   
   

80
00:09:33,347 --> 00:09:35,337
Is it a date?

81
00:09:35,337 --> 00:09:37,137
Unfortunately, not yet.

82
00:09:37,137 --> 00:09:39,617
Who is it?

83
00:09:39,617 --> 00:09:41,977
You should tell me now and confess.

84
00:09:41,977 --> 00:09:44,337
Not yet, I'll tell you later.

85
00:09:44,337 --> 00:09:46,117
Aigoo, goodness.

86
00:09:46,117 --> 00:09:49,727
What I know for sure is he's very capable and righteous.

87
00:09:49,727 --> 00:09:51,177
What?

88
00:09:51,177 --> 00:09:53,557
"R-Righteous"?

89
00:09:56,307 --> 00:10:01,337
Isn't being good at his work enough? He also has to be righteous?

90
00:10:01,337 --> 00:10:05,447
Wow, my daughter, you've got high standards.

91
00:10:05,447 --> 00:10:08,707
By chance, is he the love

92
00:10:08,707 --> 00:10:12,197
