Yes.

94
00:10:16,197 --> 00:10:17,937
I like this one.

95
00:10:17,937 --> 00:10:19,947
Isn't this one too tacky?

96
00:10:19,947 --> 00:10:22,757
This looks a lot more righteous.

97
00:10:22,757 --> 00:10:24,207
Come on, Dad.

98
00:10:24,207 --> 00:10:28,217
It wouldn't be good if you're righteous but look tacky.

99
00:10:28,217 --> 00:10:31,967
Well, then how about you just give up on righteousness?

100
00:10:31,967 --> 00:10:33,807
Geez.

101
00:10:37,277 --> 00:10:39,007
Hey, Jang Ho Woo.

102
00:10:39,007 --> 00:10:41,297
I realize you're not feeling well, but get up for a sec.

103
00:10:41,297 --> 00:10:43,757
What time is it?

104
00:10:44,647 --> 00:10:46,897
You're dating, right?

105
00:10:50,657 --> 00:10:52,047
   

106
00:10:53,797 --> 00:10:56,647
"Ho Woo, can I see you before you come into work?"

107
00:10:56,647 --> 00:10:58,457
"I have something I want to ask you."

108
00:10:58,457 --> 00:11:00,497
"I just miss you!"

109
00:11:00,497 --> 00:11:02,777
What is this? When did you guys start?

110
00:11:02,777 --> 00:11:05,567
   

